			<h1>The Erw Fawr Clubhouse</h1>
			<p>The Erw Fawr Clubhouse is in a prime location for outdoor activites 
			in the heart of the welsh mountains and with a village just down the road your not too far from civilisation at the same time.  </p>
			<h2> A Brief Description of the property</h2>
			<p>	Ground floor:
				Lounge; With armchairs, bench seating, large dining table, multi fuel burner and CD/Radio.
				Kitchen; Two cookers, microwave, three fridges, freezer, two sinks, worktops and storage area. All utensils, crockery, glasses and pots &#38;  pans provided.
				Toilets; Three separate toilets with wash basins.
				Shower room 1; Shower with toilet and wash basin
				Shower room 2; Two showers and two wash basins.
				Bedroom 1; Sleeps four (two bunks)
				Bedroom 2; Sleeps four (two bunks)
				Bedroom 3; Sleeps eight (four bunks)
				First floor - this floor is not currently accessible due to ongoing works to replace the roof:
				Large open plan area. 
				Small bedroom; Sleeps two (bunks).
				Medium bedroom; Sleeps four (two bunks).
				All beds have full size mattresses with hygienic covers.
			</p>
